## File naming
Files must be prefixed with feature name:
- ✅ `user_config_theme_bloc.dart`, `user_config_theme_event.dart`, `user_config_theme_state.dart`
- ❌ `theme_bloc.dart`, `bloc.dart`, `state.dart`
